0Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4976dc7a1e5d2fe236a05e46adaa07981a47321f","tid":2116184,"uid":273218,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:10:14.000Z","msg":"兩單零號病人<br />\n一單美國傳入<br />\n另一單內河碼頭<br />\n藍絲群只講美國傳入<br />\n唔提內河碼頭同豁免漏洞<br />\n其實所有漏洞都唔應該有<br />\n台灣仍然維持幾百單<br />\n人地二千萬人口<br />\n唔見全封關會維持唔到基本需要？"},{"pid":"0c288650a56c5246cfecd9fa46af8c6c3d0effdf","tid":2116184,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/111341566_300574507952005_1931707726788070891_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=LmqrWhi7IGYAX_2Z4Eq&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg2-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=3bc1b4b777c86b352ecc8a19f96a7383&amp;oe=5F3B7B49\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F111341566_300574507952005_1931707726788070891_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DLmqrWhi7IGYAX_2Z4Eq%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg2-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D3bc1b4b777c86b352ecc8a19f96a7383%26oe%3D5F3B7B49&h=afd07266&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07eebafb8cb23ef9ccfb2fc7631fe4b7289bb2e5","tid":2116184,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/110196360_300574534618669_4739772485706144981_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=Oe6r6q7DJngAX9cJjbk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg2-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=45845dff3298b2a24829f31cba2f9f8a&amp;oe=5F3A03C8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F110196360_30